ong time ago when we still accepted paper assignments...  like 2008</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3GTjphG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>"That's not how any of this works" meme</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zy7Fob4.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Happens way more than you'd think...</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9mJFSxu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's like mathematical impossible for you to pass but go ahead ... knock yourself out</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/yaNSLgg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Nope. Nothing we do here is "important"</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1idc1IF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>True story. Baffling. Like ever couple of weeks she'd ask again. Like some momento shit</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/O2coyum.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>You all know. It's always ....</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/INFGpge.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>It's like... you live here, it gets cold, how</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/kYMvc0Z.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Dog tax. This is Stash. She loves the snow

MOST VIRAL EDIT: I made all of these memes while my students took an exam. Its nice that genuine OC can still rise up from usersub around here!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/t9wKTIO</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[slightskew]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>So it begins</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/2i3tDIu</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Cr6SUxg.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Stay safe out there texans. Friendly advice from someone in New England, just because you have a large truck, doesnt mean you can drive as fast you want on ice.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/2i3tDIu</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[kingbudo101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Cartoon Characters in Real Life</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/UoBfn0o</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/p1xjuI5.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/v7DPQNj.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HNIExmN.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/el3aFQR.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3VfDHoK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/3ppC8nS.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/zN8mAZ1.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xvvVi1m.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/f9K06kO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span>