tps://imgur.com/a/Py6fMtl</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[SmokyDoggg]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Alright Imgur, Need Your Help.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/oRG2gDg</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/89jCi3j.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>February 26, 2020, Lukas took his life. Coming up in a few months he would’ve graduated high school. His class is trying to get him an honorary seat at graduation, but the principal of our small town school is worried about spreading the wrong message. His classmates have made this petition to help raise awareness. If you have just a minute to do so, please don’t hesitate. Every signature counts and I’ve seen Imgur do some amazing things.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Gqf0L05.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Lukas was a sophomore in high school. He was in theater (and was damn good at it) and ran cross country. What I remember about him most was he could probably recite the entire script of The Office. I swear it felt like everything he said was a nod to it. To the school, he was Baby Hudd, being the youngest of 3. I’m best friends with his oldest brother lovingly called Big Hudd. We graduated together. 

Second from the left is Baby Hud. Far right is one of his brothers, Lil Hudd.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/parP34F.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I’m so sad to say, I didn’t know him well enough personally and I know I can’t do him justice, not like he deserves. I knew him because I was friends with his brother. But, I was close to his mother. She is who found him.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/LOmxmq0.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>I will never, ever forget the way she’d hugged me and cried. A mother mourning her child.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/4Dkiqkw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Lukas had depression, but never reached out to anyone. His whole family still looks back and wonders how the didn’t notice. I know Big Hudd blames himself for not noticing. So does his mother</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RBzYJDD.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Check on your friends. Or if you’re struggling, please reach out. We will miss you.

The petition-

https://www.change.org/p/brynn-cummings-caleigh-cummings-lukas-s-graduation-chair?utm_c</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/oRG2gDg</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[grrumble]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Posting weird stuff</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/Y48IDba</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/K61BcwF.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/Y48IDba</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[DrakonRax]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>This is the way!</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/9DYl5s7</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ZgCa6J2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/9DYl5s7</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[killHACKS]]></dc:creator></item></channel></rss>